ontraceptives may be continued, but may not be as effective, during and for up to two weeks following treatment with boceprevir or telaprevir.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/292929/', '', 'Lamivudine, Paritaprevir, Glecaprevir, Tenofovir alafenamide, Maraviroc, Simeprevir, Cabotegravir, Valaciclovir, Zanamivir, Velpatasvir, Rilpivirine, More', 'Ulipristal, Estetrol', 1767369485);
